00:00:12.710 --> 00:00:14.000
Why am I sitting here looking?

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.210
We should just go
in there and look.

00:00:16.210 --> 00:00:17.540
Yeah, let's see.

00:00:17.540 --> 00:00:18.960
Let's see, man.

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.170
Oh, they got a
Corvette right there too.

00:00:21.170 --> 00:00:24.710
