Pepto-Bismol pink.

00:00:24.710 --> 00:00:26.250
[laughing]

00:00:26.250 --> 00:00:28.040
If you're sick to your
stomach and you look at this,

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:29.880
it only makes you sicker.
- Right.

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.040
So that's not good.

00:00:31.040 --> 00:00:32.250
You might throw
up in your mouth.

00:00:32.250 --> 00:00:35.540
These I find
bizarrely interesting.

00:00:35.540 --> 00:00:37.830
And that one's got
T-tops on it too.

00:00:37.830 --> 00:00:39.580
That little blue
one's kinda cool, man.

00:00:39.580 --> 00:00:41.000
Classic Tiffany.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.750
OK, that's a Tiffany.

00:00:42.750 --> 00:00:46.750
I want to see if anybody's home
before I make anybody nervous.

00:00:46.750 --> 00:00:49.420
Where's the front
door in this place?

00:00:49.420 --> 00:00:51.080
Is it through the gates?
- I think so.

00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:52.210
Here we go.

00:00:52.210 --> 00:00:54.080
- Maybe there's a bell--
- Maybe.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.880
[knocking]

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.750
Well, you know, if I
start looking at the cars,

00:01:01.750 --> 00:01:04.460
I bet you they'll come out.

00:01:04.460 --> 00:01:09.420
Excuse me, but, uh, could
you read this word for me

00:01:09.420 --> 00:01:10.790
